OL,4,C'benefit' after 100ml liquid rule U-
OL,5,Cturn
OL,7,FThe chief executive of Bradford
OL,8,FAirport () has insisted the benefits
OL,9,Fof new airport scanning technology
OL,10,F"still remain" despite the government
OL,11,Freintroducing restrictions on carrying
OL,12,Fliquids in hand luggage.
OL,14,FLBA is one of six airports which have
OL,15,Fnew next generation security
OL,16,Fcheckpoints (NGSC) in operation, which
OL,17,Fhad allowed them to scrap the 100ml
OL,18,Flimit on vessels.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/9
