OL,3,CAirport insist new scanners still have
OL,4,C'benefit' after 100ml liquid rule U-
OL,5,Cturn
OL,7,FMr Hodder said: "Even though the size
OL,8,Fof any individual liquid container is
OL,9,Flimited to 100ml, there is now no
OL,10,Flimit on the number of 100ml
OL,11,Fcontainers that you can carry in your
OL,12,F(hand) baggage at LBA.
OL,14,F"You don't have to remove liquids,
OL,15,Felectronics or electrical items from
OL,16,Fyour bag prior to screening.
OL,26,@tD@ApmtD@Fpn
