OL,3,CAirport insist new scanners still have
OL,4,C'benefit' after 100ml liquid rule U-
OL,5,Cturn
OL,7,F"So you pack your bag at home, make
OL,8,Fsure your liquids are in small
OL,9,Fcontainers less than 100ml and then
OL,10,Fyou can just load it onto the conveyor
OL,11,Fbelt and walk away."
OL,13,FThe high-tech CT scanners create a 3D
OL,14,Fimage of what is inside passengers'
OL,15,Fbags.
OL,17,FThe 100ml rule was introduced in 2006
OL,18,Ffollowing a foiled terror plot to blow
OL,19,Fup planes flying from London to the US
OL,20,Fwith home-made liquid bombs.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
