OL,5,Cturn
OL,7,FMr Hodder admitted there is some
OL,8,F"concern" about holidaymakers being
OL,9,Fconfused about the changes following
OL,10,Fthe DfT announcement.
OL,12,FBut he said the airport had not
OL,13,Fannounced the limit initially
OL,14,Fincreasing for hand luggage anyway, in
OL,15,Fthe hope of making the transition
OL,16,Feasier.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
