OL,3,CAirport insist new scanners still have
OL,4,C'benefit' after 100ml liquid rule U-
OL,5,Cturn
OL,7,F"What we're seeing is the vast
OL,8,Fmajority of customers are still
OL,9,Fbringing through liquids that are less
OL,10,Fthan 100ml. Very few are bringing
OL,11,Fthrough larger quantities," he said.
OL,13,F"As long as people continue to do
OL,14,Fthat. As long as they make sure those
OL,15,Fcontainers are less than 100ml then
OL,16,Fthe entire security process will be
OL,17,Feffective."
OL,19,FIn a statement, the Department for
OL,20,FTransport said the reintroduction of
OL,21,Flimits was a "temporary move."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
