OL,3,CAirport insist new scanners still have
OL,4,C'benefit' after 100ml liquid rule U-
OL,5,Cturn
OL,7,FAsked if he is expecting the
OL,8,Fgovernment to change the rules to
OL,9,Fchange again, Mr Hodder said the DfT
OL,10,Fstatement appears to indicate the
OL,11,F"intention" to change the limit back
OL,12,Fto two litres at a later stage, "once
OL,13,Ftheir concerns have been addressed."
OL,15,FHe said: "If I talk to some of my
OL,16,Fcolleagues in the industry perhaps
OL,17,Ftheir concern is it will never go back
OL,18,Fto two litres because on a global
OL,19,Fbasis, 100ml maximum liquid size is
OL,20,Fthe standard in just about every
OL,21,Fcountry in the world.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
