OL,3,CAirport insist new scanners still have
OL,4,C'benefit' after 100ml liquid rule U-
OL,5,Cturn
OL,7,F"The UK would have been a massive
OL,8,Foutlier at two litres so we're unsure
OL,9,Fwhat exactly is going to happen."
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,12,FTransport said: "From 0001 on Sunday
OL,13,F9th June 2024, 100ml restrictions on
OL,14,Fliquids will temporarily be
OL,15,Freintroduced for passengers travelling
OL,16,Ffrom six regional airports where Next
OL,17,FGeneration Security Checkpoints (NGSC)
OL,18,Fare in full operation.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
