OL,7,F"This temporary move is to enable
OL,8,Ffurther improvements to be made to the
OL,9,Fnew checkpoint systems and will only
OL,10,Faffect a small number of passengers.
OL,11,FFor most passengers, security measures
OL,12,Fwill remain unchanged.
OL,14,F"Passengers should continue to check
OL,15,Fsecurity requirements with their
OL,16,Fdeparture airport before travelling."
